===========
==>STEP NUM: 35
==>ACT: east
==>OBSERVATION: Corridor
The corridor turns sharply here, leading west and south.

You stop dead in your tracks.  At the sound end of the corridor you see two rather familiar figures.  They're Cybermen!

Cybermen!  The Cybermen have stolen the brain of Morbius!  The implications of this overwhelm your thoughts.  Not only do the Cybermen have the necessary technology to provide a body for Morbius, Morbius has all the knowledge of the Timelords.  This could make the Cybermen the most destructive force in the universe!

But you can't stop to think right now.  Forunately, the Cybermen haven't noticed you yet but that could change at any moment.
