On the west wall is a formidable metal door.  Above the doorway you can see a glass bubble which emits a blue glow.
Oh dear.  The floor appears to be missing in this room.  You tumble downwards...


Maintenance Shaft

There is a small metal box attached to the wall here.

The floor plate above has been swung downwards, flooding this part of the shaft with light.

You can also see an electronic landmine and a withered branch here.
